description: RECORD DELIMITER = “A”; indicates end of the header record
RECORD ID SEQUENCE NUMBER; begins with “00000001”
ACCOUNT NUMBER, including Office (3), Base Account (5), Check Digit (1)
INVESTMENT PROFESSIONAL (IP) NUMBER; NOTE: For three-character IP Numbers position 29 will be “”, effective Q4 2023.

INSTRUCTION TYPE; values include:
“EC” = Employer Contribution
“EX” = Exchange
“MF” = Mutual Fund Allocation
“PB” = Buy
“PS” = Redeem

FREQUENCY OF INSTRUCTION; values include:
“A” = Annually
“B” = Bi-monthly
“M” = Monthly
“Q” = Quarterly
“S” = Semi-annually“
” = Not applicable

AMOUNT or PERCENTAGE or SHARE INDICATOR; values include:
“A” = Amount
“P” = Percent
“S” = Share
TRANSACTION AMOUNT; required if Amount, Percentage, or Share Indicator in position 033 is “A”

TRANSACTION AMOUNT SIGN; values include:
“+” = Credit amount
“-” = Debit amount
“” = Not applicable
TRANSACTION QUANTITY; required if Amount, Percentage, or Share Indicator in position 033 above, is “S”

TRANSACTION QUANTITY SIGN; values include:
“+” = Positive quantity
“-” = Negative quantity
“” = Not applicable
CUSIP ASSOCIATED WITH TRANSACTION; for Buys and Sells only)
SYMBOL ASSOCIATED WITH TRANSACTION; for Buys and Sells only
TRANSACTION PERCENTAGE; required if Amount, Percentage, or Share Indicator in position 033 above, is “P”
NEXT INSTRUCTION EFFECTIVE DATE, in CCYYMMDD format
INSTRUCTION END DATE, in CCYYMMDD format
EXCLUSION PERIOD START DATE, in CCYYMMDD format
EXCLUSION PERIOD END DATE, in CCYYMMDD format

BUY AT NAV INDICATOR; values include:
“Y” = Yes, NAV
“N” = No, not NAV
“” = Not applicable

BUY AT NAV REASON; values include:
“A” = Dividend reinvestment trade
“B” = Trust company NAV per agreement
“E” = Self-directed brokerage account
“1” = Net asset value (NAV) transfer
“2” = Repurchase
“3” = Employee
“4” = Error correction
“5” = Wrap fee account
“6” = NAV commissionable
“7” = Commissionable defined contribution plan
“8” = Non-commissionable defined contribution plan
“9” = Section 529 account - qualified state tuition program
“0” = Other
“” = Not applicable

LOI/ROA INDICATOR; values include:
“L” = LOI
“R” = ROA
“” = Not applicable
LOI DATE; if LOI, in CCYYMMDD format

LOI/ROA VALUE SIGN; values include:
“+” = Positive amount
“-” = Negative amount
“” = Not applicable

CHARGE FEES TO, when NAV; values include:
“C” = Customer
“I” = IBD
“” = Not applicable

GROSS/NET INDICATOR; values include:
G” = Gross
N” = Net
” = Not applicable

“B” = No commission paid
“1” = Gross
“2” = Net

“5” = Death
“6” = Disability
“7” = Mandatory distribution
“8” = Systematic withdrawal
“9” = Defined contribution
“” = Not applicable

REDEMPTION FEE WAIVER CODE; values include:
“1” = STR waiver due to correction
“2” = Death
“3” = Disability

“C” = DC - loans

“H” = Plan fees / QDRO

USER ID OF PERSON WHO ENTERED (ADDED) INSTRUCTION
DATE INSTRUCTION ADDED, in CCYYMMDD format
TIME INSTRUCTION ADDED, in HHMISS format
USER ID OF PERSON WHO LAST MODIFIED INSTRUCTION
DATE OF LAST INSTRUCTION MODIFICATION, in CCYYMMDD format
TIME OF LAST INSTRUCTION MODIFICATION, in HHMISS format
DATE INSTRUCTION WAS DELETED, in CCYYMMDD format (delete date will appear once, after which the instruction will be removed from the file)
INTRODUCING BROKER DEALER (IBD) ORDER RECEIPT DATE, in CCYYMMDD format
IBD ORDER RECEIPT TIME, in HHMISS forma

“N” = No; order was not solicited by IBD

“” = Not applicable

“” = Not applicable

MAXIMUM AUTO INVESTMENT AMOUNT; for Mutual Fund Allocations only when Instruction Type in position 03-31 is “MF”
